('Seated Shoulder Extension Stretch', 'strength', '{"Latissimus dorsi","Pectoralis major"}', '{}', '{"none (bodyweight exercise)"}', '- Sit with your hands behind you, shoulder width apart. - Lock your elbows. - Scoot your feet and hips out forwards, lowering your shoulders down towards ground. - Go as far as possible to obtain a good stretch. See the video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihUAbG0e8zw', NULL, false),
('Horse Stance (Side Splits)', 'strength', '{"Gluteus maximus"}', '{}', '{"none (bodyweight exercise)"}', '- Stand as for a squat, with your feet wide and your toes pointed slightly outwards. - Gently squat into a deep, wide squat - your hips should be below your knees. - Hold for 3 to 5 seconds. - Come up under control, and repeat as needed.', NULL, false),
